content:
To normalize the provided profile data according to the specified guidelines, I'll follow the normalization instructions for each relevant field. Here's the process applied to the input profile:

### Input Profile
```json
{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "title": "Sr. Software Eng",
  "location": "San Fran, CA",
  "key_skills": [
    "Python",
    "Data Sci",
    "AWS"
  ],
  "experience": [
    {
      "company": "Tech Solutions inc",
      "title": "Lead Dev",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "March 2018",
        "end_date": "Present",
        "date_range": "5 years 7 months"
      },
      "location": "San Francisco"
    },
    {
      "company": "Innovatech",
      "title": "Jr. Developer",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "June 2015",
        "end_date": "February 2018",
        "date_range": "2 years 9 months"
      },
      "location": "Los Angeles, CA"
    }
  ]
}
```

### Normalized Profile
```json
{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "title": "Senior Software Engineer",
  "location": "San Francisco, California, United States",
  "key_skills": [
    "Python",
    "Data Science",
    "Amazon Web Services"
  ],
  "experience": [
    {
      "company": "Tech Solutions Inc.",
      "title": "Lead Developer",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "2018-03",
        "end_date": "Present",
        "date_range": "5 years 7 months"
      },
      "location": "San Francisco, California, United States"
    },
    {
      "company": "Innovatech",
      "title": "Junior Developer",
      "duration": {
        "start_date": "2015-06",
        "end_date": "2018-02",
        "date_range": "2 years 9 months"
      },
      "location": "Los Angeles, California, United States"
    }
  ],
  "normalization_notes": "Standardized abbreviations in job titles and skills; Expanded location abbreviations to full names; Standardized company suffix."
}
```

### Explanation of Changes
- **Job Titles**: "Sr." was expanded to "Senior", "Eng" to "Engineer", "Dev" to "Developer", and "Jr." to "Junior".
- **Location**: "San Fran, CA" was expanded to "San Francisco, California, United States", and "Los Angeles, CA" to "Los Angeles, California, United States".
- **Key Skills**: "Data Sci" was expanded to "Data Science", and "AWS" to "Amazon Web Services".
- **Company Names**: "Tech Solutions inc" was standardized to "Tech Solutions Inc.".
- **Dates**: Converted to ISO format (e.g., "March 2018" to "2018-03").
- **Normalization Notes**: Added to document significant changes and clarifications made during normalization.
